  <does rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</does>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">I WHAT INFORMATION DO WE COLLECT ABOUT YOU? Personal Information We collect personally identifiable information such as names mailing addresses e-mail addresses demographic information and similar information in a variety of situations including but not limited to the following i when you subscribe to one of our magazines or place an order see the section below for more information on subscriptions and orders ii when you register at one of our websites in connection with the purchase of a product publication or service iii when you enter personal information on one of our websites as a condition of participating in contests promotions or sweepstakes offered via these websites or iv when you wish to have a product or service fulfilled by a fulfillment partner who can meet the continuing needs of our customers</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

