  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Participating Vendors Some of our sites offer opportunities to make purchases online from special participating vendors On sites with online purchase opportunities for products and merchandise we will also give participating vendors the order information and authorization for the merchant bank Any time you order from a participating vendor that vendor will automatically have all the information related to the order Participating vendors may use that information to advise you directly of other products and offerings that they provide</evidence>
